title: 'The light is not lighting'
body: 'It\'s only been a week since this light got delivered from Amazon
column5: and I must say it has been a complete letdown. The product description touted its "bright and efficient illumination
column6:
but in reality, the light emitted is barely sufficient to illuminate a small corner of the room. The build quality is subpar, with flimsy materials that make the whole thing feel like it\'s about to fall apart any second. To add insult to injury, the installation process was a nightmare, as the instructions provided were vague and confusing. It\'s frustrating to spend money on a product that not only fails to meet its advertised claims but also causes unnecessary hassle. Save your money and look elsewhere for a better lighting solution.'
